	  AnnotationManagerImpl<..., CircleLayer> references CircleLayer (etc.) from
	  maps-style-ndk27, which class-parse cannot see (no cross-JAR reference support).
	  We restore them here with a raw (non-generic) extends="AnnotationManagerImpl" so that
	  inherited CRUD methods (create/delete/update, add*Listener) are accessible in C#.
	  Layer-property setters on the managers are NOT restored (they use further style types).
	-->
	<add-node path="/api/package[@name='com.mapbox.maps.plugin.annotation.generated']">
